### Login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vedran@test.com",
  "password": "test1234"
}

### Login - wrong password (should return 401)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vedran@test.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Register - duplicate email (should return 409)
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "vedran@test.com",
  "username": "vedran2",
  "display_name": "Vedran 2",
  "password": "test1234"
}

### Register - weak password (should return 400)
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "weak@test.com",
  "username": "weak",
  "display_name": "Weak",
  "password": "123"
}
